description: Visits to off-island treatment facilities dropped by almost half compared to the previous year.
title: Off-island cancer treatment for Manx patients 'operating as normal'
title_page: Off-island cancer treatment for Manx patients 'operating as normal' - BBC News
maintext: Julie Edge MHK said the drop in the figures was concerning as "the best outcome with cancer is to find it and treat it quickly and early".
